data.description:
Welcome to The Blue Crab! This home is part of a duplex and sits on a quiet street only 2 BLOCKS from beautiful Surfside Beach. 

The kitchen and bathrooms have been thoroughly renovated with brand new cabinets, granite, extra-wide fridge, dishwasher, garbage disposal, and microwave. This home also includes central AC/heat, keyless entry, two parking spaces, a furnished covered porch, balcony, shed, and large backyard space. Tile and real hardwood on the 1st floor spanning a spacious living room and brand new carpet on the 2nd floor. This is a prime location close to grocery stores, restaurants, and gas stations, so you have everything you need to enjoy comfy beachside living. 

Available for move-in immediately!

Owner pays for water, trash, and sewage. Tenant is responsible for electric.
